data.title: Oscar Olsen - 2023-24 - Men's Heavyweight Rowing
data.meta_description:
Oscar Olsen - Senior • 2023-24
Two seat in the 1V Win at the Sunshine State Invitational (Mar. 29-30)...Raced in the two seat of the 1V in the Robinson Cup win
data.text:
Senior • 2023-24

Two seat in the 1V Win at the Sunshine State Invitational (Mar. 29-30)...Raced in the two seat of the 1V in the Robinson Cup win vs. Cornell (Apr. 6)...Raced in the two seat of the 1V in the Compton Cup vs. Princeton (Apr. 20)...Two seat in the 1V at the Smith Cup win vs. Northeastern (Apr. 24)...Raced in two seat in the 1V win at the Adams Cup vs. Navy/Penn (Apr. 27)....Sat in two seat of the 1V at Eastern Sprints (May 19)...Raced in the six seat at the 2V at IRA Championships (May 31-June 2)...Six seat of the 2V in the Harvard-Yale Regatta (June 7)

Junior • 2022-23

Empacher-IRCA Scholar Athlete ... Sat in the seven seat in the Championship 8 B race at the Head of the Charles Regatta ... Rowed in the seven seat in the 2V8 that defeated Cornell at the Robinson Cup ... Competed in the seven seat for the 2V8 at the Stein Cup ... Part of the 2V8 boat (six seat) that defeated Princeton at the Compton Cup ... Sat in the two seat of the 1V8 that took down Penn and Navy at the Adams Cup ... Rowed in the seven seat in the 1V8, which beat Northeastern at the Smith Cup ... Rowed in the two seat for the 1V8 at Eastern Sprints ... Occupied the two seat in the first varsity eight boat at the IRA National Regatta ... Sat in the two seat in the 1V8 at the Harvard-Yale Regatta.

Sophomore • 2021-22

Stroked the 4V boat against Cornell … Helped the boat record a 30.0 second victory over the Big Red’s 4V crew with a time of 6:30.8 in the team’s first Spring race in three years … Stroked the 3V boat in the team’s dual with Brown on the Seekonk River … Helped guide the team to a 21.3-second victory with a time of 6:41.7 in the race … Stroked the 3V crew against Princeton … Helped guide the team to a 5.9 second victory while posting a time of 6:43.6 … Stroked the 3V boat in the regatta with Penn and Navy on the Charles River … Helped the boat post a 10.7 second win in the tri-race with a time of 5:56.9 … Stroked the 3V boat in the dual race again Northeastern on the Charles … Helped the boat post a 14-second win in the race with a time of 5:57.8 … Stroked the Crimson 3V crew at the Eastern Sprints Regatta, helping the boat to a third-place finish … Finished in second place at the IRA National Championships with the 3V crew in the boat’s four seat … Rowed in seat two on the 2V boat in the three-mile race versus Yale on the Thames.

2020-21

Did not compete due to season cancelation by the Ivy League.

First-Year • 2019-20

Sat in the eight seat for the second varsity eight at the 2019 Head of the Charles Regatta ... Did not compete in the spring due to season cancelation by the Ivy League.
